definition.value: A member of the class of cyclohexadienes that is cyclohexa-1,3-diene substituted by a 3-oxobutyl group at position 1 and by methyl groups at positions 2 and 6.
A member of the class of cycloalkenes that is cyclohexene substituted by a 2-methylpropyl group at position 3.
A 3-dodecene in which the double bond adopts a trans-configuration.
A 3-dodecene in which the double bond adopts a cis-configuration.
